{"tid":1365164,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑有物資站冚檔","createTime":"2019-07-25T14:26:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T00:27:17.000Z","uid":74379,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"73445379770792978f301feb13a83427c25d05ee","tid":1365164,"uid":74379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T14:26:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7suGuho.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7suGuho.jpg&h=21116f19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n油麻地海富苑 捉賊又唔見咁多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"499833427b646c2a3c8fae556f8795175ae8bc45","tid":1365164,"uid":4942,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:01:32.000Z","msg":"痴撚線....究竟點解黑警可以沒收d物資？？？<br />\n<br />\n犯乜野法呢？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n//大角咀今晚有人開站收集物資<br />\n主要都係急救物資同埋一啲自保裝備<br />\n例如頭盔等等<br />\n<br />\n點知突然有人報警<br />\n然後黑警派咗足足6架警車嚟收走啲物資<br />\n一認係自己嘅就抄牌<br />\n於是街坊只可以睇住一袋袋物資上晒警車<br />\n連企喺附近嘅人都被抄牌<br />\n好嬲之餘又乜都做唔到<br />\n<br />\n想提提各區物資站<br />\n收到幾袋就拎走部份先<br />\n亦要小心附近搞事嘅人<br />\n<br />\n選擇性執法已經係常態//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/okCXNBP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FokCXNBP.png&h=bbe154d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"50ec25240271856ea64eeaff41a2d6756b1ff4c7","tid":1365164,"uid":14087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:03:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eca64daaad6df81f4c07a3c7bf30af4cd8f6405","tid":1365164,"uid":10509,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:03:12.000Z","msg":"憑乜沒收人財產<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bb963809af9756285f7dcacbfabe13b8e3c1c6a","tid":1365164,"uid":279145,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:04:14.000Z","msg":"Google decathlon (TKO 店）最多貨！"},{"pid":"0b44bbea1503f1638617720e8e93656b72baa